{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":7,"day":11}],"page_start":6,"page_end":6,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"站在阶级斗争的最前线","authors":["战士翟玉堂"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心赤胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀世界革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在阶级斗争的最前线！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有枪声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在哪里战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢于刺刀见红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把敌人吓得丧胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，新的战斗打响了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化战线上号角震天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场兴无灭资的战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严重的阶级斗争摆在我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它关系到我国革命的前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它关系到世界革命的发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握紧阶级斗争的笔杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和敌人打一场近战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔也是刀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔也是枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔也是爆破筒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔也是手榴弹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出二百米硬功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出最大的勇敢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级敌人倒下了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们并没闭上双眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里攥着刀子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里揣着毒箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披着马列主义的外衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样子装得非常慈善。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想资本主义复辟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推垮人民铁打的江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们打错了算盘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江水不会倒流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的车轮岂能倒转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说什么风雨已经平息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国内外都很平安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明是叫我们解除武装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哄骗我们放下枪杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办不到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有枪杆才有政权！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么资产阶级“权威”“专家”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们早已把你们看穿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反共的老手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的逆叛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的帮凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石的鹰犬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党你们骂不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义江山你们碰不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们越骂，我们的队伍越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们越骂，我们的红旗越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上好阶级斗争的刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨亮阶级斗争的利剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛打猛攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集中火力点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同敌人战斗到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捍卫无产阶级政权。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让毛泽东思想的伟大红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在思想阵地上插遍！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（本版作品除署名的以外，由总后勤部政治部文化部供稿。）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}